# EMPATHY Official Module Scope

Product modules for the platform:

- Dashboard
- Profile
- Physiology
- Training
- Nutrition
- BioEnergetics
- Health
- Biomechanics
- Aerodynamics
- Longevity & Fitness (Longevity & Fitness Index / EPI engine + daily check-in + Empathy Coin; deterministic engine, AI interpretation only)
- Athletes (coach area)

Rules:

- Do not add `prototypes` to product navigation.
- Keep Physiology naming consistent (no legacy "Metabolic Profile/Lab" in nav).
- New feature pages must map to one of the official modules or `settings`.
- Any temporary experimental area must stay out of main navigation.
- Phase 2 "individual health" expands Health and related modules without breaking the generative loop (`docs/PHASE2_HEALTH.md`).
